e%20symptoms%20of%20postpartum%20depression.">根据疾病预防控制中心的研究</a>，八分之一的女性会出现产后抑郁症的症状。产后抑郁症的症状在出生后可能会非常严重，并且可能很危险，因为它会干扰新妈妈的生活能力。两项随机、双盲研究证明了该药物的功效，从而获得了期待已久的批准。</p><p> Zurzuvae 的一个重要特点是该药物预计在短短几天内起效，并且预计服用时间长达两周。在这种每日一次的口服药丸出现之前，产后抑郁症最常见的治疗方案需要静脉注射。这意味着需要由医院或医疗机构的医疗保健提供者进行管理。获得批准后，Zurzuvae 将能够扩大服务范围并惠及更多出院妇女。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>问题是这种药物会影响患者的驾驶能力并导致极度困倦。此外，该药物的警告标签强调，与大多数抗抑郁药一样，该药物可能会导致自杀意念的风险增加。最重要的是，Zurzuvae 还可能对胎儿造成伤害。服用该药物的患者应在服药期间以及服用 Zurzuvae 后一周内采取避孕措施。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/fda-approves-first-oral-postpartum-depression-pill-063216439.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/fda-approves-first-oral-postpartum-depression-pill-063216439.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7753b179-f7d9-4929-a182-e230ec64b289</guid><dc:creator>马拉克·萨利赫</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 05 Aug 2023 06:32:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691217137</ingested><modified> 2023-08-05T06:32:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Health Care Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Health]]></category><category><![CDATA[Pharmaceuticals & Drug Trials]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Malak Saleh]]></category><media:content height="5773" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/7f694200-3357-11ee-95fb-85e9109944e1" width="8660"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1827" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/91501520-3357-11ee-bc7e-c5cfc4a0b2a0" width="2742"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[AP]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Food and Drug Administration sign outside their offices in Silver Spring, Maryland.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Birth Control Recall]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Federal judge narrows scope of antitrust case against Google ahead of trial]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>谷歌刚刚在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-us-justice-department-antitrust-competition-announcement-144344497.html">针对该公司的一项反垄断案件</a>中获得了部分缓刑。联邦法官阿米特·梅塔 (Amit Mehta) <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/04/technology/google-search-monopoly-judge.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;referringSource=articleShare">裁定</a>，司法部 (DOJ) 和主要州不能声称谷歌通过在搜索结果中推销自己的产品而不是其他产品来保护垄断地位。根据裁决，原告尚未证明存在“反竞争效应”。梅塔法官还驳回了有关 Android 兼容性和反碎片协议、Google Assistant、物联网设备和 Android 开源项目的反垄断指控。</p><p>梅塔法官表示，司法部仍然可以提出剩余的论点。值得注意的是，官员们声称谷歌通过交易滥用权力，要求Android制造商预装谷歌应用程序并使谷歌成为其移动浏览器中的默认搜索引擎。美国司法部和各州担心这会阻碍 Bing 和 DuckDuckGo 等竞争对手获得广泛采用。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>谷歌全球事务总裁肯特·沃克在给 Engadget 的一份声明中表示，该公司欢迎法官在驳回搜索问题时的“仔细考虑”。他坚称，人们选择谷歌只是“因为它有帮助”，而且该公司将在审判中证明其其他做法既具有竞争力又合法。我们已要求司法部发表评论，如果收到回复，我们会通知您。</p><p>美国司法部和合作伙伴州于 2020 年提起诉讼。他们当时并未主张实施具体处罚，但处罚可能包括罚款、业务限制和将部门拆分为独立的公司。当时，谷歌为自己辩护，称它仍然需要谈判合作伙伴关系，并且面临来自 Twitter（现在的 X）和 Expedia 等服务的竞争。</p><p>这并不是针对谷歌的唯一反垄断案件，包括在美国。 2020 年，一个国家联盟因<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-antitrust-lawsuit-texas-attorney-general-204043354.html">涉嫌反竞争广告定价</a>而起诉谷歌。然而，缩小范围可能会使案件变得更加困难，更不用说限制潜在的损害了。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/federal-judge-narrows-scope-of-antitrust-case-against-google-ahead-of-trial-202837725.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/federal-judge-narrows-scope-of-antitrust-case-against-google-ahead-of-trial-202837725.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 619fcfc8-7f19-46c1-bb83-21db0efb0e28</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 04 Aug 2023 20:28:37 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691180920</ingested><modified> 2023-08-04T20:28:44+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="3862" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/977afb60-3300-11ee-af7b-6257b1650ab1" width="5856"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3862" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/977afb60-3300-11ee-af7b-6257b1650ab1" width="5856"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Justin Sullivan via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[MOUNTAIN VIEW, CALIFORNIA - MAY 10: Alphabet CEO Sundar Pichai delivers the keynote address at the Google I/O developers conference at Shoreline Amphitheatre on May 10, 2023 in Mountain View, California. Google held its annual Google I/O developers conference where they are expected to unveil the new Pixel Fold foldable smartphone.  (Photo by Justin Sullivan/Getty Image